				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I think that this article was really mostly directed towards the low level monks. I can't count the number of times I've been in Qeynos, Freeport or Cabilis and heard the young monks complaing and begging for money, armor or weapons. A monks life is pretty ascetic as EQ goes, you have and need nothing. <BR>
<BR>
Armor and weapons are nice if they're right for you, but they're not necessary and the newbies just don't understand it. They run around screaming about what they don't have and they don't even know that they have better bare handed skill than anybody with which to make money, exp and to get whatever they want without having to beg or rely on someone else.
				</font>
