				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hi, I have a lvl 32 monk on Cazic-Thule and just wanted to add my info here. My H2H and 1HB are both maxed for my lvl. I hit FASTER with my 2 Fighting Batons than I hit with my fists. The Batons take from 20 to about 26 dmg. My fists seem to hit slower but hit from 24 to 30 dmg. This is awesome for me, cause they seem to do about the same damage when all is said and done. Just thought I'd give this info, I have practiced 1HB since lvl 17 and have still practiced H2H also. Hope this helps, my advise is just to practice both and make you're disision after trying both. Sorry for any spelling or grammar errors, I'm in a hurry =)<BR>
<BR>
Ryuoko Hayabusa lvl 32 Monk Cazic-Thule
